{"tid":1406114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次西環手足夠抵讚","createTime":"2019-08-04T12:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:42:42.000Z","uid":69293,"like":457,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"bd490a75692c9e1ec17808a299c72ae163d258f1","tid":1406114,"uid":69293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:15:43.000Z","msg":"//今次因事未能發個夢只可做冷氣軍師，請見諒//<br />\n<br />\n我睇到直播見到手足係咁推前都擔心會出現旺角戀戰的情況，而西環尾的位置比旺角危險足足十倍，可以走後退四散的位置唔多。一但停左地鐵的時候就只係可以往山走，而圍捕的風險就大增。<br />\n<br />\n今次hit and run，等班黑狗周圍射完一輪推前少少，比街坊怒屌完之後散一散去。遠離高風險地段，又做到個效果，啲黑狗上哂gear又發洩唔到，谷左下又無得繼續，最重要係無人被圍捕。今次真係做到hit and run，值得抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d9ffae90cd484c2819ce72bb86f73703a47465","tid":1406114,"uid":36592,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"勿戀戰，不死守，不被捕，不受傷，有狗就轉場"},{"pid":"39718c1ccf05b2bc2bc35826d9202608ecb66287","tid":1406114,"uid":1731,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:23:45.000Z","msg":"撚到d狗上哂gear又出唔到火<br />\n仲要得罪埋隔離d市民<br />\n呢個就係最高境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f2cee54e3209551c837a0863f99d5ef2a798d9","tid":1406114,"uid":207087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e1ce173a10543e6719216763c8e38a57d7ce54","tid":1406114,"uid":5939,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:26:35.000Z","msg":"班狗條企緊係到 企左成個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462cc88eba2046fd00c9e350eb96dedf5163eff4","tid":1406114,"uid":286792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":